# bp0.work — Application repository rules

This git repository contains **implementation code only**. Do **not** add platform specification documents, deployment checklists, or design-suite copies here.

## Non-negotiables

| Rule | Detail |
|------|--------|
| **Scope** | Edit only files under this `application/` repository |
| **No spec files in git** | Do not create or restore `accfin/docs/` specification stubs, version history tables, or copies of numbered design documents |
| **READMEs** | Keep component READMEs limited to how to run/build that component in this repo |

When design authority is required, use the **local specification workspace** on the developer machine (outside this git root). That content is not pushed to GitHub.
